{"tid":2359260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"維拉一線隊14人感染武肺，其中10人為球員","createTime":"2021-01-08T17:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T18:17:31.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6add02a03a2228b44a45cbd5e8c5a70c2bc66a81","tid":2359260,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"據BBC記者Phil McNulty報導，阿士東維拉一線隊中有14人感染新冠，其中10名是球員。<br />\n<br />\n  阿士東維拉此前確認，包括一線隊球員和工作人員在內的多人感染新冠，球隊已經關閉訓練場。一線隊所有成員、教練甸恩-史密夫等人目前都在隔離當中。<br />\n<br />\n  此前阿士東維拉官方發佈公告，明天淩晨同利物浦的足總盃第3輪比賽，將會正常進行。"},{"pid":"6a6a766eb8dca09a46a559c627aef8aad4fc04fe","tid":2359260,"uid":248695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:10:17.000Z","msg":"青年軍都夠炒多次利記7-2<br />\n輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edfdd7badc6591445a2f6b65837e13894a1d92a","tid":2359260,"uid":248695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"維拉如果唔係俾獌狗黑而加都爭緊冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3deb7cab1d3a5f6547518b9a95ea2385d014db","tid":2359260,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"一隊中十個都唔改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}